- Video Streaming
- Disaster Recovery
- Machine Learning Datasets
- Software Downloads

📝 Key Takeaways
- Amazon S3 is an object storage service.
- Data is stored as Objects inside Buckets.
- Buckets have globally unique names.
- Maximum object size is **5 TB**.
- Amazon S3 provides **99.999999999% (11 nines) durability**.
- Supports multiple storage classes for cost optimization.
- Versioning protects against accidental deletion.
- Lifecycle Policies automate storage management.
- Encryption secures data at rest and in transit.
- Cross Region Replication improves disaster recovery.

